解题思路:
只有今天比昨天的价格高，抛售，计算总利润

![图片.png](https://pic.leetcode-cn.com/1621863132-PAKSmw-%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87.png)

* 

```
class Solution {
public:
    int maxProfit(vector<int>& prices) {

        int sum=0;

        for(int i=1;i<prices.size();i++)
        {
            if(prices[i]>prices[i-1])
            {
                sum+=prices[i]-prices[i-1];
            }
        }

        return sum;
    }
};
```

